    "en": {
      "title": "No candidate has the support of Sri Lankanpa",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Sri Lanka Freedom Party has decided not to participate in the vote to be held in the Parliament to elect a new President.",
        "Acting Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe, opposition leader Sajith Premadasa, Anura Kumara Dissanayake of the National People's Force, and Dallas Alahapperuma of the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna are scheduled to compete in the polls to elect the new President."
      ],
